<table align="center" class="content-body">
  <tr>
    <td class="content-body_wrap padding-x-40">
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <p> Hi {{name}},</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="padding-y-20">
            <p>
              We hope this message finds you well. It appears that there was an
              issue processing your payment for Business plan.
            </p>
            <p class="padding-y-20">
              To ensure uninterrupted access to ToolJetâ€™s premium features, we
