              complete by
              <span class="text-bold">{{expirationDate}} UTC</span>
              or else your business plan subscription will expire and revert
              back to basic plan.
            </p>
            {{#if (eq whiteLabelText "ToolJet")}}
              <p class="padding-y-20">
